description: Discover loft living at its finest in this 2-bed, 2-bath home at FP3, located in Seaport's lively Fort Point neighborhood. This stunning loft offers modern luxury, featuring soaring ceilings and expansive windows that fill the space with natural light. The open-concept living area integrates seamlessly with a gourmet kitchen, equipped with high-end appliances and a large island, perfect for entertaining. The primary bedroom provides a spacious and serene retreat, while the second bedroom offers versatility for guests or a home office. FP3 amenities include 24/7 concierge service, a common roof deck with stunning city views, elevator, bike storage, and an art gallery. Situated in the heart of the Seaport District, this loft is surrounded by dining, shopping, and a Trader Joes around the corner. Experience the best of urban living!
